                    <li>您同意自行承擔使用本服務之風險。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="terms-section">
                <h2>六、準據法及管轄法院</h2>
                <p>本條款之解釋與適用，以及與本條款有關的爭議，除法律或本條款另有規定者外，均應依照中華民國法律予以處理，並以臺灣臺北地方法院為第一審管轄法院。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .page-wrapper {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 60px);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
       
    }

    .terms-container {
        flex: 1;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .terms-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    .terms-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: #718355;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .terms-content {
        flex: 1;
    }

    .terms-section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .terms-section:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .intro-text {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4a4a4a;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .terms-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #6A994E;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    .terms-section ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .terms-section li {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4a4a4a;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .terms-section li::before {
        content: "•";
        color: #6A994E;
        font-weight: bold;
        position: absolute;
        left: -1.5rem;
        top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .terms-section li:hover {
        /* Removed hover effects as per privacy.cshtml */
    }

    .terms-section p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4a4a4a;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .terms-container {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem;
        }

        .terms-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .terms-header h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .terms-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .intro-text,
        .terms-section li,
        .terms-section p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style> 